<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>SQL Challenge - Grupo 4</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fira+Code:wght@400;500;600&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Outfit:wght@400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        /* ================= THEME & VARIABLES ================= */
        :root {
            --bg-dark: #030305;
            --bg-panel: rgba(12, 12, 16, 0.7);
            --bg-card: rgba(22, 22, 30, 0.6);
            --primary: #00f0ff;
            /* Neon Cyan */
            --secondary: #7000ff;
            /* Deep Purple */
            --tertiary: #ff0055;
            /* Neon Pink */
            --success: #00e676;
            --error: #ff1744;
            --text-main: #f8f9fa;
            --text-muted: #a0aab2;
            --border-light: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            --border-glow: rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.4);

            --font-heading: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
            --font-body: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            --font-code: 'Fira Code', monospace;

            --transition-smooth: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1);
        }

        /* ================= GLOBAL RESETS & SCROLLBAR ================= */
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        }

        ::-webkit-scrollbar {
            width: 6px;
            height: 6px;
        }

        ::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {
            background: var(--primary);
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--bg-dark);
            color: var(--text-main);
            font-family: var(--font-body);
            overflow: hidden;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        /* ================= DYNAMIC BACKGROUND ================= */
        .bg-effects {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            z-index: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .orb {
            position: absolute;
            border-radius: 50%;
            filter: blur(80px);
            opacity: 0.4;
            animation: float 20s infinite alternate ease-in-out;
        }

        .orb-1 {
            width: 600px;
            height: 600px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--secondary) 0%, transparent 70%);
            top: -100px;
            left: -100px;
        }

        .orb-2 {
            width: 500px;
            height: 500px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--primary) 0%, transparent 70%);
            bottom: -50px;
            right: 10%;
            animation-delay: -5s;
        }

        .orb-3 {
            width: 400px;
            height: 400px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--tertiary) 0%, transparent 70%);
            top: 40%;
            left: 40%;
            opacity: 0.2;
            animation-delay: -10s;
        }

        .grid-overlay {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background-image:
                linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03) 1px, transparent 1px),
                linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03) 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 40px 40px;
            opacity: 0.5;
            mask-image: radial-gradient(circle at center, black 40%, transparent 100%);
            -webkit-mask-image: radial-gradient(circle at center, black 40%, transparent 100%);
        }

        @keyframes float {
            0% {
                transform: translate(0, 0) scale(1);
            }

            50% {
                transform: translate(50px, 30px) scale(1.1);
            }

            100% {
                transform: translate(-30px, 60px) scale(0.9);
            }
        }

        /* ================= PRESENTATION CONTAINER ================= */
        .slide-deck {
            position: relative;
            width: 1400px;
            height: 780px;
            background: var(--bg-panel);
            backdrop-filter: blur(30px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(30px);
            border-radius: 24px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
            box-shadow:
                0 30px 60px -10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8),
                inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            overflow: hidden;
            z-index: 10;
        }

        .slide {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            padding: 60px 80px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            opacity: 0;
            visibility: hidden;
            transform: translateY(30px) scale(0.98);
            transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1), visibility 0.6s;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .slide.active {
            opacity: 1;
            visibility: visible;
            transform: translateY(0) scale(1);
            z-index: 2;
        }

        /* ANIMATIONS FOR SLIDE CONTENT */
        .slide .stagger-1,
        .slide .stagger-2,
        .slide .stagger-3,
        .slide .stagger-4 {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(20px);
            transition: opacity 0.5s ease, transform 0.5s ease;
        }

        .slide.active .stagger-1 {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
            transition-delay: 0.2s;
        }

        .slide.active .stagger-2 {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
            transition-delay: 0.35s;
        }

        .slide.active .stagger-3 {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
            transition-delay: 0.5s;
        }

        .slide.active .stagger-4 {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
            transition-delay: 0.65s;
        }

        /* ================= TYPOGRAPHY ================= */
        h1,
        h2,
        h3,
        h4 {
            font-family: var(--font-heading);
            color: var(--text-main);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 72px;
            font-weight: 900;
            line-height: 1.1;
            letter-spacing: -0.03em;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .gradient-text {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary), #a855f7, var(--tertiary));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            text-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.3);
        }

        .slide-header {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .slide-title {
            font-size: 42px;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        }

        .badge {
            background: rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.2);
            color: var(--primary);
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        .badge.purple {
            background: rgba(112, 0, 255, 0.15);
            border-color: rgba(112, 0, 255, 0.3);
            color: #b388ff;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 17px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        strong {
            color: var(--text-main);
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        /* ================= LAYOUTS ================= */
        .layout-2col {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 30px;
            height: 100%;
            overflow-y: hidden;
        }

        .layout-3col {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 25px;
        }

        .col-scrollable {
            overflow-y: auto;
            padding-right: 15px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 20px;
            padding-bottom: 40px;
        }

        /* ================= UI COMPONENTS ================= */
        .glass-card {
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 24px;
            transition: var(--transition-smooth);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .glass-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 2px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2), transparent);
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.3s;
        }

        .glass-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px -10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }

        .glass-card:hover::before {
            opacity: 1;
        }

        .card-title {
            font-family: var(--font-heading);
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            color: var(--text-main);
        }

        .card-title i {
            color: var(--primary);
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        .info-list {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .info-list li {
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 28px;
            font-size: 15px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }

        .info-list li i {
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: 3px;
            color: var(--primary);
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        /* ================= CODE BLOCKS ================= */
        .code-window {
            background: #09090b;
            border: 1px solid #27272a;
            border-radius: 14px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }

        .code-header {
            background: #18181b;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #27272a;
        }

        .mac-btn {
            width: 12px;
            height: 12px;
            border-radius: 50%;
        }

        .mac-close {
            background: #ff5f56;
        }

        .mac-min {
            background: #ffbd2e;
        }

        .mac-max {
            background: #27c93f;
        }

        .code-title {
            margin-left: 10px;
            font-family: var(--font-body);
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #a1a1aa;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .code-content {
            padding: 20px;
            font-family: var(--font-code);
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #e4e4e7;
            overflow-x: auto;
        }

        .sql-kw {
            color: #f43f5e;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        /* Pink */
        .sql-fn {
            color: #8b5cf6;
        }

        /* Purple */
        .sql-str {
            color: #10b981;
        }

        /* Green */
        .sql-var {
            color: #38bdf8;
        }

        /* Blue */
        .sql-op {
            color: #facc15;
        }

        /* Yellow */
        .sql-com {
            color: #71717a;
            font-style: italic;
        }

        /* Gray */

        /* ================= ALERTS & HIGHLIGHTS ================= */
        .alert-box {
            background: rgba(234, 179, 8, 0.1);
            border-left: 4px solid #eab308;
            padding: 16px;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }

        .alert-box.danger {
            background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1);
            border-color: #ef4444;
        }

        .alert-box h4 {
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .alert-box.danger h4 {
            color: #ef4444;
        }

        .alert-box.warning h4 {
            color: #eab308;
        }

        .alert-box p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: var(--text-main);
        }

        /* ================= FOOTER & CONTROLS ================= */
        .presentation-footer {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            padding: 20px 40px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8), transparent);
            z-index: 20;
        }

        .progress-line {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            height: 3px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            width: 100%;
        }

        .progress-fill {
            height: 100%;
            width: 0%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--primary), var(--secondary));
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--primary);
            transition: width 0.4s ease;
        }

        .slide-indicator {
            font-family: var(--font-code);
            font-size: 13px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        .nav-controls {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .nav-btn {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            color: var(--text-main);
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            transition: var(--transition-smooth);
        }

        .nav-btn:hover {
            background: var(--primary);
            border-color: var(--primary);
            color: #000;
            transform: scale(1.1);
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.4);
        }

        /* ================= GAME SHOW QUIZ STYLES ================= */
        .quiz-wrapper {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            height: 100%;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            position: relative;
        }

        .quiz-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            padding: 15px 25px;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            border-radius: 16px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
        }

        .score-display {
            font-family: var(--font-heading);
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--text-main);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .score-display span {
            color: var(--primary);
            text-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.5);
            font-size: 28px;
        }

        .question-box {
            font-family: var(--font-heading);
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            line-height: 1.4;
            color: var(--text-main);
            text-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }

        .options-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .option-btn {
            background: rgba(30, 30, 40, 0.6);
            border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: left;
            font-family: var(--font-body);
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-main);
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 16px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .option-btn::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 4px;
            height: 100%;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }

        .option-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            border-color: var(--primary);
            background: rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.05);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
        }

        .option-btn:hover::before {
            background: var(--primary);
            width: 6px;
        }

        .option-letter {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            width: 36px;
            height: 36px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: 800;
            font-family: var(--font-heading);
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        /* States */
        .option-btn.correct {
            background: rgba(0, 230, 118, 0.1);
            border-color: var(--success);
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0, 230, 118, 0.2);
            animation: pulse-correct 0.5s ease;
        }

        .option-btn.correct::before {
            background: var(--success);
            width: 100%;
            opacity: 0.1;
        }

        .option-btn.correct .option-letter {
            background: var(--success);
            color: #000;
        }

        .option-btn.wrong {
            background: rgba(255, 23, 68, 0.1);
            border-color: var(--error);
            animation: shake 0.4s ease;
        }

        .option-btn.wrong::before {
            background: var(--error);
        }

        .option-btn.wrong .option-letter {
            background: var(--error);
            color: #fff;
        }

        .option-btn.disabled {
            pointer-events: none;
            opacity: 0.6;
        }

        .option-btn.correct.disabled {
            opacity: 1;
        }

        @keyframes shake {

            0%,
            100% {
                transform: translateX(0);
            }

            20%,
            60% {
                transform: translateX(-10px);
            }

            40%,
            80% {
                transform: translateX(10px);
            }
        }

        @keyframes pulse-correct {
            0% {
                transform: scale(1);
            }

            50% {
                transform: scale(1.05);
            }

            100% {
                transform: scale(1);
            }
        }

        /* Explanation Box */
        .explanation-box {
            background: rgba(112, 0, 255, 0.1);
            border-left: 4px solid var(--secondary);
            border-radius: 0 12px 12px 0;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            display: none;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.5s ease;
        }

        .explanation-box h4 {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
            color: #b388ff;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .explanation-box p {
            margin: 0;
            color: #e4e4e7;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .next-q-btn {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--secondary));
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            padding: 14px 28px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 800;
            font-family: var(--font-heading);
            cursor: pointer;
            align-self: flex-end;
            display: none;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(112, 0, 255, 0.3);
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        .next-q-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px) scale(1.02);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.4);
        }

        /* Results Screen */
        .results-screen {
            display: none;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 100%;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .score-circle {
            width: 200px;
            height: 200px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: conic-gradient(var(--primary) var(--progress, 0%), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05) 0);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            position: relative;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 50px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.2);
        }

        .score-circle::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            width: 170px;
            height: 170px;
            background: var(--bg-panel);
            border-radius: 50%;
        }

        .score-text {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 10;
            font-family: var(--font-heading);
            font-size: 56px;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: #fff;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <!-- Abstract Tech Background -->
    <div class="bg-effects">
        <div class="orb orb-1"></div>
        <div class="orb orb-2"></div>
        <div class="orb orb-3"></div>
        <div class="grid-overlay"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="slide-deck">

        <!-- SLIDE 1: PORTADA -->
        <div class="slide active" id="slide-1">
            <div
                style="height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center; text-align: center;">
                <div class="stagger-1 badge" style="margin-bottom: 30px;">Laboratorio U4 - 19/05/2026</div>
                <h1 class="stagger-2">SQL Challenge: <br><span class="gradient-text">Joins, Filtros y
                        Agregaciones</span></h1>
                <p class="stagger-3" style="font-size: 22px; max-width: 800px; margin-top: 10px; color: #d4d4d8;">
                    Análisis profundo de las estructuras de consulta del proyecto.
                </p>
                <div class="stagger-4" style="margin-top: 60px; display: flex; gap: 30px;">
                    <div class="glass-card" style="padding: 15px 30px; text-align: center;">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-code-merge"
                            style="color: var(--primary); font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 10px;"></i>
                        <div style="font-weight: 700; color: #fff;">Uniones</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="glass-card" style="padding: 15px 30px; text-align: center;">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-filter"
                            style="color: var(--secondary); font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 10px;"></i>
                        <div style="font-weight: 700; color: #fff;">Filtros</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="glass-card" style="padding: 15px 30px; text-align: center;">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-calculator"
                            style="color: var(--tertiary); font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 10px;"></i>
                        <div style="font-weight: 700; color: #fff;">Agregaciones</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- SLIDE 2: JOINS AVANZADOS -->
        <div class="slide" id="slide-2">
            <div class="slide-header stagger-1">
                <span class="badge">Eje 1</span>
                <h2 class="slide-title">Uniones Relacionales (Joins) y Patrones</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="layout-2col">
                <div class="col-scrollable stagger-2">
                    <p style="margin-bottom: 20px;">Dominar los JOINs va más allá de unir tablas. Implica comprender
                        cómo el motor de bases de datos genera relaciones entre conjuntos de datos mediante productos
                        cartesianos y posteriormente aplica filtros basados en condiciones lógicas y matemáticas.</p>

                    <div class="glass-card" style="border-color: var(--primary);">
                        <h3 class="card-title"><i class="fa-solid fa-bolt"></i> El Patrón "Anti-Join"</h3>
                        <p style="font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;">Una de las preguntas más comunes en bases de
                            datos es:<br>
                            <strong>¿Cómo encontrar clientes que nunca han realizado una compra?</strong>
                        </p>
                        <p style="font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 15px;">Muchos usan <code>NOT IN</code>, pero este
                            método puede ser lento y además presentar problemas cuando existen valores NULL. Por eso,
                            una mejor práctica es utilizar el patrón Anti-Join, que combina <code>LEFT JOIN</code> con
                            <code>IS NULL</code>.
                        </p>

                        <div
                            style="background: #09090b; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; font-family: var(--font-code); font-size: 13px;">
                            <span class="sql-kw">SELECT</span> c.nombre<br>
                            <span class="sql-kw">FROM</span> clientes c<br>
                            <span class="sql-kw">LEFT JOIN</span> facturas f <span class="sql-kw">ON</span> c.id =
                            f.cliente_id<br>
                            <span class="sql-kw">WHERE</span> f.id <span class="sql-kw">IS NULL</span>;
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-scrollable stagger-3">
                    <div class="glass-card" style="border-color: var(--secondary); height: 100%;">
